data.description: Welcome to the sought after neighborhood of Merry Point Estates! Enjoy your coffee on the back deck of this beautiful unique house, just steps from the James River.  Approximately $70,000 worth of renovations in the past two years with receipts provided, including work on the HVAC system, roof and electrical.  Termite clear letter done. Pick up your clubs and head over to the nearby country club for a round with friends.  After a long day, enjoy a soak in the hot tub overlooking the water.  Peaceful bliss. You are home.
